&lt;li&gt;Draft, negotiate, and structure commercial agreements, including MSAs, SOWs, NDAs, and partnership agreements with enterprise and Fortune 500 clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain contract templates, playbooks, and self-service resources that enable efficient deal flow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on data privacy and regulatory compliance, including HIPAA, GDPR, CCPA, and SOC 2 requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage employment law matters across multiple jurisdictions, including handbooks, policies, and workplace investigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee corporate governance, entity management, and international subsidiary compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and mitigate legal and business risks; advise leadership on risk exposure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support M&amp;amp;A activity, commercial real estate transactions, and other corporate matters as they arise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
