&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;J.D. from an accredited law school; active bar admission&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8 + years of legal experience, with significant in-house technology experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commercial contracts expertise, particularly in software/ technology services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to lead cross-functional projects beyond traditional legal scope&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent judgment, communication skills, and executive presence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable operating with autonomy in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
